snippet.title: The Rodinia Project - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Rodinia Project is a tranquil first-person sci-fi puzzle adventure.

You find yourself in front of a huge structure surrounded by the ocean, alone. Manipulate the environment and overcome challenges to ascend the Nexus and discover the mysteries of these strange installations.

Buy on Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/681520

www.therodiniaproject.com
